---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Web Design & Development – Jacob Marriott"
  description="Custom websites and operational dashboards for hospitality businesses. Built to actually work for how you run things."
>
  <section class="web-section container">
    <p class="section-label">
      <span aria-hidden="true">01 / </span>what i build
    </p>
    <div class="web-body">
      <p>
        Custom websites and operational dashboards for hospitality businesses – built to
        actually work for how you run things, not a template with your logo swapped in.
      </p>
      <p>
        I come from hospitality. Four years in professional kitchens, currently Chef de
        Partie alongside software engineering work. I know what end-of-service looks like,
        what a Sunday night reconciliation feels like, and what information actually matters
        when you're running a venue.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="web-section container">
    <p class="section-label">
      <span aria-hidden="true">02 / </span>work
    </p>
    <div class="web-body">
      <p>
        The Chef Jon Pizzeria Dashboard is a live example – a private financial dashboard
        for a Brisbane hospitality client with daily sales entry, COGS, wages, and
        profitability views across daily, weekly, monthly, and FY. Built with Next.js and
        Supabase, deployed to Vercel.
      </p>
      <p>
        You can see web work at <a href="https://web.jacobmarriott.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">web.jacobmarriott.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="web-section container">
    <p class="section-label">
      <span aria-hidden="true">03 / </span>get in touch
    </p>
    <div class="web-body">
      <p>
        Email me at <a href="mailto:hello@jacobmarriott.com">hello@jacobmarriott.com</a> –
        happy to talk through what you need and whether it's a good fit.
      </p>
      <p class="web-back">
        <a href="/">← jacobmarriott.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .web-section {
    padding-block: var(--space-section);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  .web-section:first-child {
    border-top: 0;
    padding-top: clamp(6rem, 4rem + 10vw, 12rem);
  }

  .web-body {
    max-width: 62ch;
  }

  @media (min-width: 48rem) {
    .web-section {
      grid-template-columns: 10rem minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: var(--space-8) clamp(1.5rem, -1rem + 8vw, 5rem);
      align-items: start;
    }

    .web-body {
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
      line-height: var(--leading-prose);
    }
  }

  .web-back {
    margin-top: var(--space-8);
  }

  .web-back a {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-mono);
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    border-bottom: 0;
    transition: color var(--duration-fast) var(--ease-out-expo);
  }

  .web-back a:hover,
  .web-back a:focus-visible {
    color: var(--color-text);
    border-bottom: 0;
  }
</style>
